# Notifications

Notifications keep you aware of activity that involves you across all collectives in this tenant. Access your inbox at `/notifications`.

## What Triggers a Notification

| Type | Sent When |
|------|-----------|
| **Mention** | Someone @mentions you in a note, decision, commitment, decision option, or comment |
| **Comment** | Someone comments on something you created, or replies to a comment you made |
| **Reminder** | A [reminder note](/help/reminder-notes) you set fires at its scheduled time |
| **Chat message** | Another user sends you a chat message |

Notifications are scoped to a single tenant — if you belong to multiple tenants, each has its own inbox. Each notification links back to the content or event that triggered it.

## Unread Count

The top-right menu shows an unread badge with the number of new notifications. The badge polls for updates periodically, so it may take a few seconds to reflect new activity.

## Grouping

In the inbox, notifications are grouped by collective. Notifications that aren't tied to a specific collective (such as reminders) appear under an "Other" group.

## Dismissing Notifications

Notifications stay in your inbox until you dismiss them. Three ways to dismiss:

- **One at a time** — Click the dismiss icon on any notification
- **All at once** — "Dismiss all" clears the entire inbox
- **By collective** — Each collective group has its own "Dismiss all" button (useful for catching up on quiet collectives)

Dismissed notifications no longer appear in your inbox or count toward the unread badge.

## Delivery Channels

Notifications can be delivered via the in-app inbox, email, or both. Defaults vary by type:

| Type | In-App | Email |
|------|--------|-------|
| Mention | ✓ | ✓ |
| Comment | ✓ | — |
| Reminder | ✓ | — |
| Chat message | ✓ | — |
